{"tid":1096421,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"床蝨定過敏？","createTime":"2019-04-07T16:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T17:24:05.000Z","uid":94075,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6bcad7ca12dec1b89add0c3d36ee4141b5d673f5","tid":1096421,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"由前日開始就有啲紅腫嘅粒粒 起初以為比蚊咬因爲住得低層 但又唔覺夜晚有蚊啲聲 點知琴日又有一粒 今日又有一粒 之前試過間房有床蝨但治左大半年 有噴過de粉同埋佢啲結晶我冇清走等啲後患都死埋 但今次啲咬痕係得一粒 唔似之前咁一次過有幾粒<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日我起身都有少少鼻敏感(其實好左好多年但空氣唔好會鼻塞打乞痴) 同埋慣左夜訓 兩三點甚至四點先訓 塊面都爆左好多瘡 會唔會其實係我抵抗力差左過敏？但一日一粒過敏？<br />\n<br />\n全能嘅連登仔 可否解答我嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb79374689e3e68bbf3fad88efe4df443325a791","tid":1096421,"uid":245106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:40:56.000Z","msg":"有冇圖睇睇 好似蟲咬 有分別 <br />\n跳蚤 就三點紅 <br />\n有圖最佳"},{"pid":"7fc1da0f48145f2d57c246b5cc8d907502bef352","tid":1096421,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Druznvx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDruznvx.png&h=39d8f5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/voRenvz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvoRenvz.png&h=93c9b673&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAFbpJW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAFbpJW.png&h=699aea74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a30d9e1f186b96a86022a0666d68be03e2da4607","tid":1096421,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"似敏感"},{"pid":"f5dba588ded4d6bb6cf049e2e5c4762cf91fd434","tid":1096421,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb79374689e3e68bbf3fad88efe4df443325a791","tid":1096421,"uid":245106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:40:56.000Z","msg":"有冇圖睇睇 好似蟲咬 有分別 <br />\n跳蚤 就三點紅 <br 